<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id90f6ad45-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6" identifier="/us/usc/t22/s8175"><num value="8175">§ 8175.</num><heading> Notice of IAEA notifications</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The President shall notify Congress of any notifications issued by the IAEA to the United States under Article 10 of the Additional Protocol.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id90f6ad46-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">(<ref href="/us/pl/109/401/tII/s275">Pub. L. 109–401, title II, § 275</ref>, <date date="2006-12-18">Dec. 18, 2006</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/120/2753">120 Stat. 2753</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
